PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782839907
OL,3,CFamily make emotional appeal to help
OL,4,Cfind woman, 29, last seen in Cornwall
OL,6,FShe was wearing a hospital gown, a
OL,7,Fgreen jumper and trainers with black
OL,8,Fand yellow bags underneath used as
OL,9,Fsocks. She had a white plastic bags
OL,10,Fwith her and a black Takamine acoustic
OL,11,Fguitar.
OL,13,FAfter leaving hospital police believe
OL,14,FHolly boarded a bus carrying her
OL,15,Fguitar and a hospital crutch, wearing
OL,16,Fthe bags under her shoes and carrying
OL,17,Fa clear bag of belongings. Holly is
OL,18,Fknown to travel using Cornwall's bus
OL,19,Fnetwork.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
