PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782839907
OL,3,CFamily make emotional appeal to help
OL,4,Cfind woman, 29, last seen in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe day before she went to The Royal
OL,7,FCornwall Hospital, she is seen on CCTV
OL,8,Fin Tregolls Road, Truro having come
OL,9,Fvia a stop at St. Columb Road.
OL,11,FShe is wearing large, shaped
OL,12,Fsunglasses, blue Jeans, a large black
OL,13,Fcap, carrying a black guitar and a
OL,14,Flight-coloured canvas type handbag.
OL,16,FPolice Staff Investigator Joanne
OL,17,FWilson said: "Sadly, Holly has now
OL,18,Fbeen missing for three whole months.
OL,26,@yD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
