OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782839907
OL,3,CFamily make emotional appeal to help
OL,4,Cfind woman, 29, last seen in Cornwall
OL,6,F"She was cold and had no shoes on her
OL,7,Ffeet. She went to Treliske Hospital at
OL,8,Fthat time and thereafter her movements
OL,9,Fare unknown. We would like to hear
OL,10,Ffrom anyone who may have seen her on
OL,11,Fthe bus leaving Treliske towards
OL,12,FNewquay at just after 11am on 30th
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,F"If anyone who has any information on
OL,16,Fher whereabouts or her travels on or
OL,17,Fafter 30th or 31st March are
OL,18,Fencouraged to call in on 101 quoting
OL,19,F50260109918."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@MO]
